Text: That core... Target the glimmer within!
A scorching festival of flame! You two made for excellent kindling!
With friends like you, there's snow end to the fun!

You poisoned princes
suited your slimy transformation!
Keep your spirits up! We're making good progress!
I daresay greater foes await us...
The guardian of this place... Let us make quick work of it!
Behold the mark of the sun─an arbiter of Azeyma!
I know it's hard to envisage, but there'll soon be a magnificent base right here!
The assignment is simple: clear the site of obstructions and tend to construction tasks!
Solid foundations, check. Eager contributors, check. Cosmoliner construction awaits!
Though we must first tend to the mini rovers. Go forth and recharge their depleted battery packs!
Contributors, are you ready? Our goal: a homely, heartwarming habitation module!
Of course, we'll need to make sure the mini rovers are fully charged before work begins in earnest!
If our interstellar aspirations are to get off the ground, we'll need a place to launch them! Time to build a cosmoport!
Alas, our fleet of mini rovers grows listless! Recharge them so that work may commence!
Time for an upgrade of galactic proportions!
Retrieve the components you need and assemble them on-site. Remember, only the highest quality will suffice!
Right, we're digging a tunnel clear through this place!
It'll be a tough job, so get ready to roll up your sleeves and put your back into it!
The ground here needs to be leveled in preparation for the lift. Your orders are to dig, collect, carry, and repeat!
It's a colossal task, but the more hands we have, the lighter the work will be!
We need to expand our energy generation facilities! Your job will be to monitor the mini rovers.
Keep an eye out for drained battery packs─get them recharged and back into the rovers as quickly as possible!
Next on the agenda is the expansion of our water supply systems! Our mini rovers are assembled and ready for this crucial task.
But a rover without power might as well be a paperweight, so make sure to keep those battery packs charged!
This is it─the final project! Let's get building!
Not far now. Keep up the pace!
When we're finished building on these foundations, we'll have the most cosmotastic hub you can imagine.
The assignment is simple: clear the site of obstructions and tend to construction tasks!
An elixir!? Oh rapture! Oh joy!
It seems we must clear a path through these creatures.
Indeed. Let us proceed with caution.
Now to put my time training on the beach to good use!
The sand has built up over the long years...
Has it been using this chamber as its lair...?
Hmph. What a vexing creature that was.
To think it was clever enough to use the pipes and sand to its advantage...
We knew it wouldn't be easy. Let's stay strong and keep going!
Is he testing us against that mechanical soldier?
Fine by me. If he wants a show, let's give him one!
It was following orders... Does an even fiercer machine await us?
Gah! They came out of nowhere!
I don't believe it intends to let us pass...
All the more reason to see just what lies beyond.
What is that? A floating rock?
Something's carved into it... Alexandria's emblem, perhaps?
Is it moving along the pipes?
I don't think it's trying to flee...
It means to catch us by surprise!
What are we up against now?
Remain calm─we can evade its attacks!
No doubt it will fight to the last...
Steel your nerves and make ready to dodge!
We must fight our way through.
The airships are taking heavy damage. We must do something!
I'm glad you're safe. Come, let's keep moving.

Issue no warnings.
Proceed to elimination.
I can barely feel my legs...

I don't want to die...
Don't let me die...
We won't let you harm our charges!
\\<snicker> What'd you get done for, then?
We'll show you how it works around here!
We've got just the tools for the job.

You'll make a fine example!
Get 'em!

Keep going!
If we can just make it to the keep...
Their legs may tremble, but our hearts are steady!
If only I could fight better...
For each accused, a fitting punishment!
The hour of the condemned is nigh...

No more!
I can't take any more...
I-I have to get away from here...

Catch me if you can!
I'll make it worth your while!

What's the matter?
I'm over here, meow!

How dare you ignore me!
I'm leaving, meow.

Gonna take me on, huh!?
Then give me all you got, meow!

Over here!
Just try and catch me!

Initiating guest protocol...
Welcome! Here for fabulous prizes?
Should you require my services, do not hesitate to call!
So much to do! Yes, so very much!

It appears my services are unrequired.
If you'll excuse me...
You have business with me? Very well!
Wanton violence shall not be tolerated!
Dear guests, you must stop this folly at once!
That appears to be the last of them.
The currents will carry us. Come!

For my family!
For my people!

Let's keep moving!
Sareel Ja has to be here somewhere.
What did he do to us!?

Stay calm.
We fight through it.

Careful!
He means to use that spray!

The numbing spray!
Watch out, everyone!

Brace yourselves!
He readies his toxic spray!

Very well.
I will fight you myself.
The others...can handle themselves, I'm sure.
Hm. Hoping to divide and conquer?
A new stage for us to fight on...

The Endless...
You go too far, Calyx!
I don't like the looks of this!

By the sunken gods...
Everything's burning...

Another change...
Along with new threats, I expect.

And again!
The lightning's getting worse!
The fear of these Endless is palpable...
We will bring an end to this, I promise you!

Test us again and again.
You will not find us wanting!

The center of the battlefield!
We bear it together!
Perhaps some magic in the mix.
Have you the strength to find the answers you seek?
Ah, we've got quite the crew gathered here! Together we shall build a base from which we will explore every corner of this star!
First we'll have to build the foundation so our facilities can be properly anchored to the glass surface. Make sure to vacuum up the glass dust before it piles up!
Our next step is to build the Cosmoliner! Once our research team can zip back and forth across Phaenna, we'll be able to ramp up our exploration!
Leave the complicated assembly and welding to the mini rovers. Your job is to put the finishing touches to the Cosmoliner's components!
Homey, comfortable habitation modules will help us house more eager workers! Let's get started!
Time to put together the frames and flooring for the habitation modules! Leave assembly and welding to the mini rovers!
Further exploration will require even more energization! These facilities will allow us to convert ambient aether into usable electricity!
Take care of the mini rovers, and they'll do the dangerous work for you! A perfect working relationship!
In the vastness of space, water is an invaluable resource! Building hydrofication stations will allow us to extract and purify underground water!
The purification system is full of highly conductive and intricate parts─a job for the mini rovers, methinks!
All right, it's time to reinforce this area of the base! When we're done, it'll be safer and more cosmotastic than ever before!
Keep a careful eye on the glass foundation, but don't let our other work fall by the wayside!
Once the crane network and walkways are installed, we'll be able to delve into the depths of the crater!
You can see how far down the glass flows, eh? Down there an entirely new environment awaits intrepid explorers! Gets your heart pounding, doesn't it?
The cosmoport is good, but we can make it great! Soon our ships will convey us to the furthest reaches of the firmament!
To start, we'll need to build a dedicated power supply! The first step towards a brighter future for space travel!
If we want to give our mechs the care they deserve, then we'll need to give the hangar a cosmotastic upgrade!
Idle machinery is at the mercy of Phaenna's harsh clime, but we can fortify it! Improved maintenance facilities certainly wouldn't hurt, either!
Ready to work? Good! These panels will allow us to collect and store Phaenna's naturally occurring energy!
Namely, they gather the rays of light in the atmosphere and convert them into electricity! Once the panels are in place, our energy problems will become a thing of the past!
The drones are freezing the molten glass to give you all a surface to walk upon!
However, it's up to you lot to find the hottest points so we can move in!
Our base here on Phaenna is as good as finished! All that's left is the finishing touch─the Stellascope!
This marvelous work of engineering will allow us to peer into space's darkest corners! And it'll be our job to keep it spick-and-span!

To the middle!
We close ranks!
So this is what it looks like inside...
Calyx will have prepared us a warm welcome.
This is a different floor to where I was in stasis.
We fight our way straight to the top!
Calyx awaits us at the very top, then?
What in the...? Everything has changed!
This is the Alexandria of my time!
Ah. He's adjusted the electrope to project a new appearance.
He's quite literally setting the scene.
Even within his stronghold, he leverages the fear of death...
He must be modifying their memories to set them against us.
He has them believing we are invading enemies...
He would force a healer to fight us!?
He seems quite serious about barring our path.
Yet another Endless being made to see us as the foe.
We've no choice but to fight if we're to proceed.

Steel your hearts.
We must forge onward.
There are cracks in the electrope.
Didn't we pass a terminal like that already?
Should we take a look at that terminal?
Should we stop and take a quick look?
Big lads...and there are four of them.
This will be no easy battle.
This is an execution chamber, then...

It happened again.
Look at the walls!
Memories are not tools to be exploited...
We cannot allow this to continue.
This is putting enormous stress on the electrope...
We are not done, it seems...
Is this a game to him?
He's forcing the Endless to relive their memories of war...
There looks to be a way inside.
We must be nearing the top by now!
This way if we want to continue upwards.
Then what are we waiting for!?
You make a mockery of their suffering!
So many memories in one place...

The Endless...
I can feel their terror.
He's fused them into a single entity...

Stop this!
Haven't they suffered enough!?
This one looks like a challenge!
The quicksand will lead us onwards.
Her soldiers certainly arrived en masse.
This place is rife with vilekin... Where hides the chimera?
Its reign of terror ends now!
Each of its three heads is deadly─take care!
This beast has slain so many...
Limited though we may be, we defy you nonetheless!
Your plans end here with you!

Eurgh!
Keep your hands off me!

Watch the arms!
They betray the intent!
Not good! I need to move away!
Lead it away from the group!

Ungh!
The sheer strength of it...

The aether gathers again...
A different shape this time!
So that's what that shape means!

The stored aether...
Its effects can be delayed.
It's bringing some new attack to bear!
The ground... Where did it go!?
How do we deal with this!?
Do not be fooled by the movements.

Keep a clear head.
We can handle this.
Over to the edge and hunker down!

Destroy them!
Quickly as you can!

Be strong!
We can take it!

Well, that was exciting...
Back to it, then!
It wants to drag us into the abyss.
It means to discharge in rapid succession!
A successive pattern, as we suspected.
Together, we can undo its magicks!
Watch out for those giant hands!
Work is progressing better than I could've imagined! Keep up the pace!
We're only a hop, skip, and a jump away from our goal! One final push─for the initiative!
Our task is to build a housing unit for drones capable of cooling molten glass.
We hope to forge a safe path across Fusingway Vent in the name of exploration─but for that, we require a mobilization station!
With this crane construction, we may finally pave a path to the chasm!
